text: Yevhen Tsymbalyuk (; born 19 June 1996 in Krasnyi Lyman, Donetsk Oblast, Ukraine) is a professional Ukrainian football defender who currently plays for FC Olimpik Donetsk in the Ukrainian Premier League. Tsymbalyuk is a product of the FC Olimpik Donetsk Youth School System. He made his debut for FC Olimpik in the match against FC Illichivets Mariupol on 30 May 2015 in the Ukrainian Premier League. == References == ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:FC Olimpik Donetsk players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players Category:Association football forwards
